overview:
AsianWeddings.ca is the complete wedding solution for today’s South Asian market: Punjabi, Indian, Pakistani, Fijian, Bengali, and Sri Lankan. We connect businesses to consumers through our Wedding Planner (published every year) and online Wedding Planner (e-Planner).

Our cutting edge content provides brides, grooms, and their families with the latest asian and indian wedding trends and customs while remaining focused on the history and traditional values of Asian Weddings, whether it is the Anand Kaaraj, Vivaah, Nikaah, or Civil Ceremony.

The Vendors Directory helps asian brides, grooms, and their families to find products or services such as bridal wear, jewellery, catering and more. AsianWeddings.ca is part of an elite group of companies that has been in publication since 1995. Our ability to understand the printing and publication industry allows us to value the exclusive needs and demands of the Asian Community. As a vendor, your business will gain maximum exposure to the Asian Community through our many publications. The mission of AsianWeddings.ca is to be the first to implement an extensive Wedding Planner and thorough e-Planner in the Asian Community.
